---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="SSOSC Case Study">
  <Navigation />

  <main id="main-content" class="flex-1 max-w-[68ch] mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24 flex flex-col gap-12 font-sans">
    
    <!-- Top Bar Navigation -->
    <div class="text-xs text-[#71717A] font-mono border-b border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] pb-4">
      <a href="/work" class="hover:text-[#FAFAFA] transition-colors">← Back to Work</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="flex gap-2 text-xs text-[#71717A] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">
        <span>Community</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>2024</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-medium text-[#FAFAFA] tracking-tight leading-tight">
        SSOSC
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] italic">
        "A student-run open source community platform built to share learning repositories and host hackathons."
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Project Snapshot -->
    <section class="border-y border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] py-6 text-xs font-mono text-[#A1A1AA] flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div>Role: <span class="text-white">Co-founder & Organizer</span></div>
      <div>Duration: <span class="text-white">Jan 2024 – Dec 2024</span></div>
      <div>Status: <span class="text-white">● Maintained</span></div>
      <div>Team: <span class="text-white">2 Engineers</span></div>
      <div>Stack: <span class="text-white">Next.js · GitHub API · Vercel</span></div>
      <div>Repository: <span class="text-white">Open Source</span></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Study Sections -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 text-[#FAFAFA] text-base leading-[1.7] tracking-tight font-normal">
      
      <!-- 1. Executive Summary -->
      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">01. Executive Summary</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]">
          SSOSC (Symbiosis Student Open Source Community) is a web hub built to coordinate open source learning workshops, maintain student code repositories, and list local hackathon events. The project focused on lowering contribution barriers for beginners.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 2. Goals -->
      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">02. Goals</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]">
          The goal was to build a clean index of student projects and active repositories, utilizing the GitHub API to showcase code contributions and keep student logs updated automatically.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 3. Architecture -->
      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">03. Architecture</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]">
          The site was built using a Next.js static setup, fetching active organization repository metadata via build-time GitHub API requests and caching parameters on edge CDNs.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 4. Challenges -->
      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">04. Challenges</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]">
          Handling GitHub API rate limits during concurrent static build triggers required configuring build caches and fallback stale content data models.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 5. Outcome -->
      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">05. Outcome</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]">
          The platform helped coordinate three local hackathons, indexing dozens of open student projects and supporting hundreds of active open contributions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 6. Lessons -->
      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">06. Lessons</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA]">
          I learned that building community platforms requires designing simple contributor boundaries. Decoupling the codebase and documenting the deployment setup allows other students to contribute fixes easily.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Tech Stack footer (mono, last) -->
    <footer class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-[#71717A] border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] pt-6 mt-4">
      <span>Technologies: Next.js · GitHub API · Tailwind CSS · Vercel</span>
    </footer>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
